comment: Gordon (HOU) firms up his position and sets the screen on Roberson (OKC), absorbing the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Oladipo (OKC) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Adams (OKC) clamps Ariza's (HOU) arm and affects his ability to defend the play.
Roberson (OKC) makes marginal contact with Beverley (HOU) during rebounding.
Westbrook (OKC) jumps backwards and initiates the marginal contact with Gordon (HOU).
Grant (OKC) makes contact with the ball after it touches the backboard.
Westbrook (OKC) makes contact with the ball in the frontcourt, causes it to go into the backcourt, and then recovers the ball.
Oladipo (OKC) makes incidental contact with Gordon (HOU) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Gordon (HOU) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact with Harden (HOU) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Roberson (OKC) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Harden (HOU) off of the backboard.
Gordon (HOU) jumps from point A to point B into the body of Westbrook (OKC) and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Westbrook (OKC) was attempting a 2pt field goal when fouled is confirmed.
Roberson (OKC) makes marginal contact with Harden (HOU) that does not affect his SQBR.
Ariza (HOU) legally contests Westbrook's (OKC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Nene (HOU) and Adams (OKC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Westbrook (OKC) makes body to body contact with Gordon (HOU) that affects his SQBR.
Ariza (HOU) makes contact with Westbrook (OKC) that affects his SQBR.
Nene (HOU) and Adams (OKC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Adams (OKC) briefly grasps Nene's (HOU) jersey but does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Adams (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Harden (HOU) that does not affect his SQBR.
Adams (OKC) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
